sequenceDiagram
    participant User as VS Code User
    participant Ext as Extension
    participant Server as local-review Server
    participant Browser as Browser UI

    Note over Ext: Activation
    Ext->>Ext: featureDetector.getFeatureId()
    Ext->>Server: GET /api/features/:id/code-session
    Server-->>Ext: { threads: ReviewThread[] }
    Ext->>Ext: commentManager.loadThreads()
    Ext->>Server: WebSocket connect /ws

    Note over User: Create new comment
    User->>Ext: Click "+" on line 42
    User->>Ext: Type comment, submit
    Ext->>Server: POST /api/features/:id/code-session/threads
    Server->>Server: Append thread, write JSON
    Server-->>Ext: 201 Created
    Server->>Browser: WS: review:session-updated
    Browser->>Browser: Re-render threads

    Note over Browser: Browser creates thread
    Browser->>Server: POST /api/features/:id/code-session/threads
    Server->>Server: Append thread, write JSON
    Server->>Ext: WS: review:session-updated
    Ext->>Ext: threadMapper.reconcile()
    Ext->>Ext: Dispose all → recreate from fresh data

    Note over User: Resolve thread
    User->>Ext: Click "Resolve"
    Ext->>Server: PATCH /:id/code-session/threads/:threadId
    Server-->>Ext: 200 OK
    Server->>Browser: WS: review:session-updated
